name: Rocket’s Tricky Gym
effect: Each Pokémon with Dark or Rocket’s in its name (both yours and your opponent’s) can use attacks on this card instead of its own.
author: Ryo Ueda

attacks.name: Feint Attack
attacks.effect: Does 20 damage to 1 of your opponent’s Pokémon. This attack’s damage isn’t affected by Weakness, Resistance, Poké-Powers, Poké-Bodies, or any other effects on that Pokémon.
